column2: SELECT top #  s.specobjid, s.bestobjid, s.firstrelease, s.survey, s.sourcetype, s.class,  gal.ra, gal.raErr, gal.dec, gal.decErr, s.z, s.zErr,  gal.dered_g, gal.dered_r, gal.dered_i, gal.modelMag_g, gal.modelMag_r, gal.modelMag_i, gal.psfMag_r, gal.extinction_g, gal.extinction_r, gal.extinction_i,   gal.petroMag_r, gal.petroR5#_r,   w.w1mpro INTO mydb.LRG_WISE FROM specobj as s   JOIN galaxy as gal on gal.objid = s.specobjid  JOIN wise_xmatch as wx on wx.sdss_objid = gal.objid  JOIN wise_allsky as w on wx.wise_cntr = w.cntr WHERE  (gal.modelfluxivar_r & gal.modelfluxivar_i & gal.modelfluxivar_z) != #   and (gal.fiber2mag_z - gal.extinction_z <= #)  and (gal.dered_i >= # and gal.dered_i <= #)  and (gal.dered_z <= #)  and (w.w1mpro != #)  and ( (w.w1mpro + #) <= #)  and (gal.dered_r - gal.dered_i > #)  and ((gal.dered_r - w.w1mpro) > # * (gal.dered_r - gal.dered_i))  and (gal.dered_i - galdered_z > #)
